# 20 - Language Translator with Context
# Translate with cultural/contextual awareness

NAME translator
INPUT source_file
INPUT target_language
INPUT context DEFAULT "general"

GOAL read "Read content from $source_file."
GOAL analyze "Analyze the text: identify idioms, cultural references, tone, and domain-specific terms for $context context."
GOAL translate "Translate to $target_language preserving meaning, tone, and cultural appropriateness."
GOAL review "Review translation for: accuracy, naturalness, and handling of untranslatable concepts."

RUN translate USING read, analyze, translate, review
